    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA315-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu talaimakaṉaip parattai nontu colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is what the other women said about HIM, being in pain.</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA315">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            īṇṭuperun teyvat tiyāṇṭupala kaḻinteṉap</l>
<l>            pārttuṟaip puṇari yalaittaliṟ puṭaikoṇṭu</l>
<l>            mūttuviṉai pōkiya murivā yampi</l>
<l>            nallerutu naṭaivaḷam vāytteṉa vuḻavar</l>
<l>            pulluṭaik kāviṟ ṟoḻilviṭ ṭāṅku</l>
<l>            naṟuvirai naṉpukaik koṭāar ciṟuvī</l>
<l>            ñāḻaloṭu keḻīiya puṉṉaiyaṅ koḻuniḻaṉ</l>
<l>            muḻavumutaṟ piṇikkun tuṟaiva naṉṟum</l>
<l>            viḻumitiṟ koṇṭa kēṇmai novvitiṟ</l>
<l>            ṟavaṟunaṟ kaṟiyā yāyi ṉempōṉ</l>
<l>            ñekiḻtōṭ kaluḻnta kaṇṇar</l>
<l>            malartīyn taṉaiyar niṉṉayan tōrē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O man from the ghat, where they fetter to the drum-trunk</l>
<l rend="indent2">with rich shade of the Puṉṉai tree joined with small-blossomed Ñāḻal,</l>
<l rend="indent">the boat with curved mouth, that had gone to work of old(?),</l>
<l rend="indent2">taking the blows of the waves slapping against the huge ghat,</l>
<l rend="indent3">since many of the years of the great god here had passed by,</l>
<l rend="indent">without giving [it] good smoke of swift fragrance,</l>
<l rend="indent2">[just] as the ploughmen, since the good bull had passed beyond fitness</l>
<l rend="indent3">in gait<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">vaḷam vāy</term>: here we have a semantic problem, since actually we would expect this phrase to mean something like "to be excellent in prosperity". Since, however, <term xml:lang="ta">vāy</term> also has a meaning of "to surpass" we might surmise that here the bull has surpassed the zenith of its strength (with reference to <term xml:lang="ta">naṭai</term>, its gait).</note>,</l>
<l rend="indent">let [it] go from [its] task in the grassy grove,</l>
<l rend="indent3">if you do not know well the mistake, thinly(?),</l>
<l rend="indent2">in the intimacy taken excellently and well(?), like us,</l>
<l>those that longed for you might be as blossoms burned,</l>
<l rend="indent">their eyes dimmed [and] shoulders emaciating.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
